---
title: Irish Beef Meatball & Roast Veggie Stew with Garlic Panini & Parsley
description: Dive into a bowl of pure comfort with this hearty stew straight from inspired from Ireland. Beef meatballs are drenched in a
tomato and red wine-based stew, and accompanied by garlic-kissed panini to soak up all the delicious sauce. With a flourish of
parsley on top, this dish will have your taste buds doing an Irish jig!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65bad5f323af27a6dfb3129b-7d5f3c96.jpeg
